{"text_id":163375,"tokens":["The"," importance"," of"," the"," merging"," activity"," for"," the"," kinetic"," polarization"," of"," the"," Sun","ya","ev","-","Zel","'","do","vich"," signal"," from"," galaxy"," clusters","."," We"," investigate"," the"," role"," of"," galaxy"," cluster"," mergers"," in"," determining"," the"," polarization"," properties"," of"," the"," Sun","ya","ev","-","Zel","'","do","vich"," (","SZ",")"," signal",","," which"," is"," a"," key"," probe"," of"," cluster"," physics"," and"," cosmology","."," Motiv","ated"," by"," the"," growing"," recognition"," of"," the"," impact"," of"," mergers"," on"," SZ"," signal"," profiles",","," we"," aim"," to"," quantify"," their"," effects"," on"," the"," kinetic"," polarization"," of"," the"," signal","."," Our"," simulations"," reveal"," that"," mergers"," significantly"," alter"," the"," polarization"," fraction"," and"," angle"," of"," the"," SZ"," signal",","," with"," the"," resulting"," kinematic"," distortions"," shaping"," the"," observed"," polarization"," patterns","."," We"," find"," that"," merger","-","induced"," asym","metries"," can"," lead"," to"," significant"," departures"," from"," the"," expected"," thermal"," polarization"," spectrum",","," which"," can"," potentially"," impact"," the"," extraction"," of"," cosmological"," parameters"," from"," SZ"," observations","."," Our"," results"," highlight"," the"," need"," to"," incorporate"," merger","-","driven"," polarization"," effects"," into"," future"," SZ"," signal"," simulations"," and"," analysis",","," enabling"," the"," precise"," character","ization"," of"," galaxy"," cluster"," properties"," and"," the"," refined"," constraints"," on"," cosmological"," models","."," By"," addressing"," this"," long","-","standing"," issue",","," we"," provide"," a"," crucial"," step"," towards"," the"," comprehensive"," understanding"," of"," the"," thermodynamic"," and"," dynamical"," properties"," of"," galaxy"," clusters","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"llama3-8b","label":1}